    {
      "title": "Investigation Queries (BigQuery)",
      "description": "Reference queries for entity-level investigation in BigQuery.",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 16 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Trace a single entity\n```sql\nSELECT entity_id, trace_id, prediction,\n  feature_fetch_latency_ms,\n  feature_fetch_retry_count,\n  prediction_retry_count,\n  processing_time, prediction_timestamp\nFROM `ml_dataset.iris_predictions_streaming`\nWHERE entity_id = '<ENTITY_ID>'\nORDER BY prediction_timestamp DESC\nLIMIT 10;\n```\n\n### Slow predictions (retries involved)\n```sql\nSELECT entity_id, trace_id,\n  feature_fetch_latency_ms,\n  feature_fetch_retry_count,\n  prediction_retry_count,\n  processing_time\nFROM `ml_dataset.iris_predictions_streaming`\nWHERE prediction_timestamp > TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 1 HOUR)\n  AND (feature_fetch_retry_count > 0 OR prediction_retry_count > 0)\nORDER BY feature_fetch_latency_ms DESC;\n```\n\n### Dead letters in last hour\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM `ml_dataset.dead_letters`\nWHERE timestamp > TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 1 HOUR)\nORDER BY timestamp DESC;\n```"
      }
    }
